text: Mía Maestro (born June 19, 1978) is an Argentine actress and singer- songwriter. She was born in Buenos Aires. Maestro is known for her role as Nora Martinez in The Strain, Nadia Santos in the television drama Alias, as Christina Kahlo in Frida, and as Carmen in The Twilight Saga.Mía Maestro Fansite ==References== ==Other websites== * *Mia Maestro official website Category:1978 births Category:Living people Category:Argentine movie actors Category:Argentine television actors Category:Singers from Buenos Aires Category:Writers from Buenos Aires Category:Actors from Buenos Aires
